---
title: Easy Creamy Chicken, Bacon & Parmesan Spaghetti with Spinach & Rocket Salad
description: This creamy spaghetti concoction comes together in a snap! With golden nuggets of crispy bacon and baby leaves stirred through for a touch of vibrant green, the beauty is in the simplicity of this meal. Sprinkle over a generous amount of Parmesan cheese and a pinch of chilli flakes if you’re feeling feisty!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/676ceb881ca370104ed06de2-56e96bb9.jpeg
